OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers. The showers
OL,8,Fbecoming less frequent and lighter
OL,9,Fthrough the course of the night. Touch
OL,10,Fof frost possible in sheltered spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,13,Fa mix of sunny spells and showers, the
OL,14,Fshowers heavy at times. Winds turning
OL,15,Fnortherly and becoming strong at times
OL,16,Fnear the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
